From the manufacturer

AmazonBasics Stainless-Steel Stock Pot with Lid

A useful cooking vessel for any kitchen, this AmazonBasics Stainless-Steel Stock Pot with Lid holds up to 8 quarts at a time and offers exceptional versatility. Use the large pot for anything from cooking family-size batches of soups, stews, and chili to boiling water for summertime canning.

Durable and Fast Heating

The stock pot features heavy-gauge stainless-steel construction for stability and strength, and its encapsulated aluminum base distributes heat quickly and evenly.

Induction-Friendly & Oven-Safe

The cookware can be used on any stovetop, including induction. With the lid removed, it's oven-safe up to 500 degrees F.

Details

  • 8-quart capacity
  • Stainless-steel construction
  • Encapsulated aluminum base
  • Riveted side handles
  • Glass lid with steam hole
  • Suitable for any stovetop
  • Oven-safe (with lid removed)
  • Dishwasher-safe

Riveted Side Handles

The AmazonBasics stock pot comes equipped with riveted stainless-steel side handles for reliable strength when lifting or transporting the cookware from the sink to the stovetop and back again.

Glass Lid Included

The AmazonBasics stainless-steel stock pot includes a see-through tempered-glass lid that traps heat, moisture, and flavor during the cooking process. The lid's small hole helps release steam, and its transparent design allows for checking the status at a glance.

How customer reviews and ratings work

Customer Reviews, including Product Star Ratings help customers to learn more about the product and decide whether it is the right product for them.

To calculate the overall star rating and percentage breakdown by star, we don’t use a simple average. Instead, our system considers things like how recent a review is and if the reviewer bought the item on Amazon. It also analyzed reviews to verify trustworthiness.
